OL,3,CGP 'tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith fake covid booster jab'
OL,6,FOur reporter Katie Cole has been in
OL,7,Fcourt today.
OL,9,FA GP has gone on trial accused of
OL,10,Ftrying to kill his mother's partner by
OL,11,Finjecting him with poison while
OL,12,Fdisguised as a community NHS nurse
OL,13,Fdelivering a covid booster.
OL,15,FDr Thomas Kwan is accused of
OL,16,Fattempting to murder Patrick O'Hara in
OL,17,Fhis Newcastle home in January as part
OL,18,Fof an elaborate plot to secure the
OL,19,Finheritance of his mother's estate.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/15
