OL,3,CGP 'tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith fake covid booster jab'
OL,6,FThe prosecution alleges the scheme
OL,7,Finvolved the 53-year-old sending fake
OL,8,FNHS letters and text messages before
OL,9,Fdonning a disguise so convincing he
OL,10,Ffooled his own mother.
OL,12,FA jury at Newcastle Crown Court was
OL,13,Ftold Kwan, a practising GP and partner
OL,14,Fat Happy House Surgery, in Sunderland,
OL,15,Fadmits administering a noxious
OL,16,Fsubstance but denies attempted murder
OL,17,Fand an alternative charge of causing
OL,18,Fgrievous bodily harm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
