OL,6,FOpening the prosecution's case, Peter
OL,7,FMakepeace KC said: "Sometimes,
OL,8,Foccasionally perhaps, the truth really
OL,9,Fis stranger than fiction."
OL,11,FHe continued: "From November 2023 at
OL,12,Fthe latest, and probably long before
OL,13,Fthen, (Kwan) devised an intricate plan
OL,14,Fto kill his mother's long-term
OL,15,Fpartner, a man called Patrick O'Hara.
OL,17,F"On any view that man had done
OL,18,Fabsolutely nothing to offend Mr Kwan
OL,19,Fin any way whatsoever.
