OL,6,F"He was however a potential impediment
OL,7,Fto Mr Kwan inheriting his mother's
OL,8,Festate upon her death."
OL,10,FMr O'Hara had been in a relationship
OL,11,Fwith Kwan's mother, Jenny Leung, for
OL,12,Fmore than 20 years, jurors were told.
OL,14,FShe named Mr O'Hara in her will to the
OL,15,Feffect that he could stay in her house
OL,16,Fin St Thomas Street, Newcastle, should
OL,17,Fshe die before her partner.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]
