OL,6,FThat decision led to her having a
OL,7,Fstrained relationship with her son, so
OL,8,Fmuch so that the police were called
OL,9,Fwhen Kwan burst into her home
OL,10,Funinvited in November 2022, the court
OL,11,Fwas told.
OL,13,FA year later, Kwan, who is married
OL,14,Fwith a son and lived 50 miles south in
OL,15,FBrading Court, Ingleby Barwick,
OL,16,FTeesside, faked a letter from the NHS
OL,17,Fon his home computer to Mr O'Hara
OL,18,F"with chilling authenticity", Mr
OL,19,FMakepeace said.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@\O]
