OL,6,FClaiming to be from a community nurse
OL,7,Fcalled Raj Patel, he offered Mr O'Hara
OL,8,Fa home visit, following up that letter
OL,9,Fin January.
OL,11,FMr Makepeace said: "As, I suspect,
OL,12,Fwould any of us, Mr O'Hara fell for it
OL,13,Fhook, line and sinker, he had not the
OL,14,Fslightest suspicion that this was
OL,15,Fanything other than a genuine NHS
OL,16,Fcommunity care initiative which he
OL,17,Fwarmly welcomed and was grateful for."
