OL,6,FThe court heard that in the early
OL,7,Fhours of 22 January this year, Kwan
OL,8,Fdrove his car - using a fake
OL,9,Fregistration plate - from his family
OL,10,Fhome to a Premier Inn, in Newcastle,
OL,11,Fwhere he had booked a room under a
OL,12,Ffalse name.
OL,14,FHe was captured on CCTV, shown to the
OL,15,Fcourt, leaving his room, wearing a
OL,16,Flong coat, hat, clinical mask and blue
OL,17,Fsurgical gloves.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/15
