OL,6,FFootage tracked the GP making his way
OL,7,Fon foot to the city centre home his
OL,8,Fmother shared with her partner of more
OL,9,Fthan 20 years.
OL,11,FCCTV footage released by Northumbria
OL,12,FPolice shows Dr Thomas Kwan arriving
OL,13,Fin Newcastle before putting on a
OL,14,F"disguise"
OL,16,FMr Makepeace said the 72-year-old let
OL,17,Ftinted-glasses-wearing Kwan into the
OL,18,Fhouse where he spent 45 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/15
