OL,6,FDuring this time, Kwan spoke in what
OL,7,Fthe court heard was broken English
OL,8,Fwith an Asian accent and told Mr
OL,9,FO'Hara he needed a covid booster, even
OL,10,Fthough he had only had one three
OL,11,Fmonths ago.
OL,13,FHe took blood samples from Mr O'Hara,
OL,14,Fchecked the blood pressure of both him
OL,15,Fand Ms Leung, and then injected Mr
OL,16,FO'Hara's arm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/15
