OL,3,CGP 'tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith fake covid booster jab'
OL,6,FThe court was told Mr O'Hara suspected
OL,7,Fsomething was wrong as the pain
OL,8,Fworsened - and a comment made by Ms
OL,9,FLeung that the apparent nurse was the
OL,10,Fsame height as her son.
OL,12,FAfter Kwan left the home, Mr O'Hara
OL,13,Fsought medical help and spent weeks in
OL,14,Fintensive care.
OL,16,FMr Makepeace said: "It quickly became
OL,17,Fapparent Mr O'Hara was suffering from
OL,18,FNecrotising Fasciitis, that is a rare
OL,19,Fand life-threatening, flesh-eating
OL,20,Fdisease.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/15
