OL,3,CGP 'tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith fake covid booster jab'
OL,6,F"Over the coming days Mr O'Hara
OL,7,Funderwent a series of surgical
OL,8,Finterventions as plastic surgeons and
OL,9,Fother specialists worked to stem the
OL,10,Fspread of the disease by cutting away
OL,11,Fthe diseased flesh and the margins of
OL,12,Fthat flesh with the healthy, in the
OL,13,Fhope of removing the source of
OL,14,Finfection as it was spreading.
OL,16,F"Very considerable portions of Mr
OL,17,FO'Hara's arm flesh had to be removed
OL,18,Fin repeated procedures."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUzD@XO]
