OL,6,FThe jury heard that two weeks after
OL,7,Fthe visit, Kwan was arrested by police
OL,8,Fwho found a haul of chemicals and
OL,9,Fassociated equipment in a detached
OL,10,Fgarage.
OL,12,FA search of his home also revealed a
OL,13,Fmobile phone used to text Mr O'Hara
OL,14,Fand storage devices containing
OL,15,Fresearch materials on poisons,
OL,16,Fguidance on murder investigations, and
OL,17,Ftoxicology books including a book
OL,18,Fcalled '10 poisons used to kill
OL,19,Fpeople'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/15
